═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="cd-faq">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true">
          <i class="fas fa-minus icon-open"></i><i class="fas fa-plus icon-closed"></i>
          How long does enterprise software development take?
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a" style="display:block;">Enterprise projects vary widely. A focused internal tool may take 3–4 months; a full ERP replacement can span 12–18 months. We provide a detailed phased roadmap after discovery so you have clear milestones and predictable delivery.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
          <i class="fas fa-minus icon-open"></i><i class="fas fa-plus icon-closed"></i>
          Can you modernize our existing legacy system?
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">Yes. We assess your current system, document business logic, and design a migration path that preserves what works while replacing what doesn't — minimizing risk through phased transitions rather than high-risk big-bang replacements.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
          <i class="fas fa-minus icon-open"></i><i class="fas fa-plus icon-closed"></i>
          How do you handle enterprise security requirements?
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">Security is designed in from the start. We implement role-based access control, audit logging, encryption at rest and in transit, and compliance controls aligned with your specific regulatory obligations — SOC 2, HIPAA, GDPR, or others.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
          <i class="fas fa-minus icon-open"></i><i class="fas fa-plus icon-closed"></i>
          Do you integrate with systems like SAP, Salesforce, or Workday?
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">Absolutely. We have experience integrating with major enterprise platforms through their official APIs, webhook systems, and middleware connectors, building reliable data flows that sync in real time or on schedule.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
          <i class="fas fa-minus icon-open"></i><i class="fas fa-plus icon-closed"></i>
          What happens after the software launches?
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">We offer structured support and maintenance agreements — from on-call incident response to dedicated development retainers — ensuring your system stays secure, performant, and aligned with your business as it evolves.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

